text: Blokhino () is a rural locality (a village) in Akberdinsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 41 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 58 km from Iglino, 3 km from Akberdino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Blokhino
